\par INSTALLING THIS UPDATE
\par 
\par * This update can not be applied to Delphi 7 Architect Trial
\par   version.
\par   
\par * This update can not be removed after it is installed.
\par 
\par * You will need the original Delphi 7 installation CD available
\par   to install this update.
\par 
\par * To install this update from the CD, insert the CD, and launch
\par   the d7_ent_upd1.exe file appropriate for your locale.
\par 
\par * To install this update from the Web, double-click the 
\par   self-executing installation file and follow the prompts.
\par   
\par * The Delphi 7 documentation PDF files are available on
\par   the update CD.
\par 
\par ========================================================
\par 
\par UPDATING LOCALIZED VERSIONS OF DELPHI 7
\par 
\par * This update can be applied only to the English version of
\par   Delphi 7. There are separate updates for the German, French
\par   and Japanese versions of Delphi 7.
\par  
\par * This update provides new localized versions of the SqlConst
\par   files. After installing the update, backup and delete the
\par   following files from the Delphi 7 installation folder:
\par   
\par   Lib\\Debug\\SqlConst.dcu
\par   Lib\\SqlConst.dcu
\par   Source\\Vcl\\SqlConst.pas
\par   
\par   and then remove the appropriate locale extension (.de, .fr, or
\par   .jp) from the new SqlConst files in the same folders. For
\par   example, for the French version of Delphi, rename
\par   SqlConst.dcu.fr to SqlConst.dcu.
\par   
